Class WikiSearchProvider

All Implemented Interfaces:
KeywordSearchProvider, SearchProvider, SparqlSearchProvider
public class WikiSearchProvider
extends AbstractSparqlSearchProvider
implements KeywordSearchProvider

Search provider implementation for the Wiki indexing repository. Only processes SPARQL SELECT queries, transforms keyword queries to SPARQL using the wikiQuerySkeleton parameter.
